<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contract killers are so uncivilized.</font>

297
00:13:25,610 --> 00:13:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brought it upon yourself.</font>

298
00:13:27,090 --> 00:13:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the problem with torturers!</font>

299
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,540
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#303030">Let's build a <font color="#ea3574">fun, 
