00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero...</font>

327
00:14:30,930 --> 00:14:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't do it!</font>

328
00:14:32,330 --> 00:14:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Torture's more important 
