339
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to try dating?</font>

340
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was serious, too.</font>

341
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, why don't we try it, then?</font>

342
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, "then"?</font>

343
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:33,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else would it mean?</font>

344
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I had a job come in, 
so I'm gonna head out.</font>

345
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

346
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I won't be able to 
take time off for a while.</font>

347
00:15:52,950 --> 00:15:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

348
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Siu-san's asking 
for me, so I'm gonna go.</font>

349
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, today—</font>

350
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

351
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't go today.</font>

352
00:16:14,930 --> 00:16:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to. I'm sorry, Manika.</font>

353
00:16:21,370 --> 00:16:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

354
00:16:28,020 --> 00:16:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know exactly why he dumped me.</i></font>

355
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

356
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sitll love him!</font>

357
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

358
00:16:43,490 --> 00:16:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should you have turned 
her down like that?</font>

359
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

360
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My work and this place are still</font>

361
00:16:51,520 --> 00:16:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the most important to me. 
That won't change.</font>

362
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, there are lots of girls,
but you only get one calling.</font>

363
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

364
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Manika-chan, you're on a rampage.</font>

365
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something happen?</font>

366
00:17:14,080 --> 00:17:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

367
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe-san! Can we do a cool pose?</font>

368
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything's fine.</font>

369
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, you're being 
way too lazy about this.</font>

370
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So are you.</font>

371
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should do it.</font>

372
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are the photos for?</font>

373
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm planning to use these 
to introduce our employees.</font>

374
00:17:40,140 --> 00:17:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on a sec.</font>

375
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know we had a website!</font>

376
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just for the look of it at first.</font>

377
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now that some promising 
rookies have joined us,</font>

378
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He said we're promising!</font>

379
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there are more jobs we can take on.</font>

380
00:17:50,340 --> 00:17:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah!</font>

381
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the perfect opportunity 
to appeal to those looking for jobs!</font>

382
00:17:54,370 --> 00:17:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I want all of you to help.</font>

383
00:17:56,670 --> 00:17:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

384
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe-san, let's do it!</font>

385
00:17:59,340 --> 00:18:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

386
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pain.</font>

387
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you won't do it?</font>

388
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'll do it.</font>

389
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, first...</font>

390
00:18:07,730 --> 00:18:10,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please tell me again 
why you applied here.</font>

391
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I liked that there wouldn't be much 
need to meet people face-to-face.</font>

392
00:18:14,930 --> 00:18:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Short hours, high pay, and curiosity!</font>

393
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's easy to understand. I like it.</font>

394
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a type of work 
I'd never done before.</font>

395
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! That's a good one!</font>

396
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I lined up a bunch of them 
and threw darts to pick one.</font>

397
00:18:26,740 --> 00:18:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a break.</font>

398
00:18:28,210 --> 00:18:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was approached by a suspicious 
person in a back alley.</font>

399
00:18:31,210 --> 00:18:33,590
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#0e0c10">Suspicious 
Person</font></font></b></font>

400
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san...</font>

401
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike and Hugh's reasons are good,</font>

402
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but is there a way to bring out 
a little more personal flair?</font>

403
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about mine?</font>

404
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the worst one.</font>

405
00:18:40,650 --> 00:18:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

406
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:43,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most torturers start on a whim.</font>

407
00:18:44,810 --> 00:18:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

408
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't there some more convincing reason?</font>

409
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, you've always loved 
the idea of torture,</font>

410
00:18:51,250 --> 00:18:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or you wanted to do it so 
badly you couldn't stand it?</font>

411
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would like someone like that, though?</font>

412
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

413
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:04,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then, why do you 
keep doing this work?</font>

414
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I have a talent for it.</font>

415
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These two are no good.</i></font>

416
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things like, "The human body is this 
sturdy?" and "This part bends, too?"</font>

417
00:19:13,180 --> 00:19:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every day is filled with the
wonders of the human body!</font>

418
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's exciting and happy, happy work!</font>

419
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He seems like he's having 
fun, but he's scary.</i></font>

420
00:19:20,460 --> 00:19:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pulling the truth out of filthy beasts 
and contributing to society...</font>

421
00:19:24,420 --> 00:19:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a very worthwhile job!</font>

422
00:19:27,050 --> 00:19:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That sounds like a good 
answer, but he's scary!</i></font>

423
00:19:29,340 --> 00:19:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't use that as-is.</font>

424
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll soften and water it down 
as much as I can first.</font>

425
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A wise choice.</font>

426
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're taking photos inside 
the torture rooms, too?</font>

427
00:19:39,190 --> 00:19:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I might be able to 
use them for something.</font>

428
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought Noe-san was scarier, 
but he's a nice guy, huh?</font>

429
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

430
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should be enough.</font>

431
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, both of you. 
You were a huge help!</font>

432
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squee!</font>

433
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san?</font>

434
00:19:58,150 --> 00:20:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem pretty fired up about this.</font>

435
00:20:00,350 --> 00:20:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really.</font>

436
00:20:01,660 --> 00:20:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just that this is about all I can do.</font>

437
00:20:04,690 --> 00:20:08,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we started this company 
with just the three of us,</font>

438
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there are lots more 
people involved now.</font>

439
00:20:10,650 --> 00:20:13,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It... makes me sort of happy.</font>

440
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san?</font>

441
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san?!</font>

442
00:20:26,320 --> 00:20:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. You done?</font>

443
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now.</font>

444
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you can have this.</font>

445
00:20:32,540 --> 00:20:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

446
00:20:33,770 --> 00:20:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Uh...</font>

447
00:20:36,130 --> 00:20:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A bribe?</font>

448
00:20:37,190 --> 00:20:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Write "Sero-sama is a genius" 
on my introduction page.</font>

449
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I'd write that.</font>

450
00:20:43,360 --> 00:20:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I don't like my coffee black.</font>

451
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't drink it? What a little baby.</font>

452
00:20:48,650 --> 00:20:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I can drink it!</font>

453
00:20:56,630 --> 00:20:57,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noe?</font>

454
00:20:57,690 --> 00:20:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still awake?</font>

455
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

456
00:21:00,410 --> 00:21:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone was kind enough 
to answer my questions,</font>

457
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I wanted to write it all up today.</font>

458
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't push yourself too hard.</font>

459
00:21:08,570 --> 00:21:10,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

460
00:21:10,280 --> 00:21:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You looked like you were 
having fun with everyone.</font>

461
00:21:12,570 --> 00:21:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made me feel better.</font>

462
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Having a place where you 
belong is nice, right?</font>

463
00:21:18,650 --> 00:21:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've had a place to belong all this time.</font>

464
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:23,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The place where I belong is with you.</font>

465
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like it?</font>

466
00:21:25,490 --> 00:21:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

467
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me. Let's try being a family.</font>

468
00:21:34,390 --> 00:21:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so silly.</font>

469
00:21:36,090 --> 00:21:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can have as many places 
to belong as you want.</font>

470
00:21:39,320 --> 00:21:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Spirytus isn't a place 
that I just handed to you.</font>

471
00:21:44,130 --> 00:21:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You built it yourself.</font>

472
00:21:46,370 --> 00:21:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hela-san...</font>

473
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, keep on making lots 
of cozy places for yourself.</font>

474
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will.</font>

475
00:21:57,460 --> 00:22:00,290
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#19181d">The Next Day</font></b></font>

476
00:22:00,290 --> 00:22:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Noe! Get over here for a sec.</font>

477
00:22:03,100 --> 00:22:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's less cozy with that in here, 
so can I toss it out?</font>

478
00:22:06,390 --> 00:22:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you just say?!</font>

479
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may not.</font>

